title: Prison Mutiny (1943) EDWARD NORRIS ♣ JOAN WOODBURY

sources.title: Prison Mutiny (1943) EDWARD NORRIS ♣ JOAN WOODBURY
sources.description:
Stars: Edward Norris, Joan Woodbury, Jack La Rue 
 Director: Phil Rosen

 Playboy Johnny Gray is framed and sent to prison after his stolen car is found at a holdup. Stung by the injustice, when even his fiancée believes him guilty, Johnny becomes an unruly prisoner and is put in a cell with the head of a prison gang planning a break!
